snippet.title: EVERSPACE™ Xbox One Pre-Alpha Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description: EVERSPACE™ is a single-player rogue-like space shooter combining top-notch visual with rogue-like gameplay elements and non-linear storytelling. It is brought to you by ROCKFISH Games, makers of the critically acclaimed “Galaxy on Fire” series, and will launch exclusively for Xbox One end of 2016.
